00:30:32.080 --> 00:30:32.376
And I could see my name tag.

00:30:37.520 --> 00:30:37.751
I could see my wife's.

00:30:37.751 --> 00:30:43.919
I could see every single one of these places that were made for every single one of us.

00:30:47.360 --> 00:30:47.900
And it was all by our heart's desire.

00:30:47.900 --> 00:30:58.029
Whatever is inside of you, what you're believing for, the greatest expectation, ladies and gentlemen, God has it inside there, and He's going to bring it to pass.

00:30:58.029 --> 00:30:58.689
Watch.

00:31:01.657 --> 00:31:05.360
And as I saw they were getting over to the side, I could see Jesus and he was riding on a white horse.

00:31:05.360 --> 00:31:10.799
There was jewels all on the side of this horse's bridle, all around his ears.

00:31:13.966 --> 00:31:14.389
And it was jewels.

00:31:19.543 --> 00:31:21.547
The most beautiful jewels—the world in all the finest jewelry stores that you've ever seen cannot compare to what I saw.

00:31:21.547 --> 00:31:32.149
The massive diamonds and the rubies and the sapphires, the beautiful splendor of heaven and the jewelry around this horse's bridle.

00:31:32.159 --> 00:31:41.543
He was up there just like he always is with that beautiful cloak on.

00:31:41.543 --> 00:31:48.339
His crown has a beautiful black and white embroidery around it with purple on top and jewels all over his crown.

00:31:48.339 --> 00:31:54.906
His cape has purple and it has this black and white thing that I saw around it.

00:31:57.639 --> 00:32:00.949
And it has this tassel that buttons it up here that's all fine jewelry and it's handcrafted.

00:32:00.949 --> 00:32:02.102
It's gorgeous.

00:32:02.102 --> 00:32:07.167
Gorgeous, the way that the stuff goes around his cloak.

00:32:16.719 --> 00:32:23.307
And he was riding on the horse and I could see on these streets of gold, there was the most beautiful streets of gold.

00:32:33.645 --> 00:32:43.634
And he was riding down this street, but there was people with banners that were on the side of the street that had 'King of Kings and Lord of Lords' all on the side of these banners.

00:32:43.634 --> 00:32:51.440
And they were dripping in purple, the most beautiful, brilliant purple I've ever seen with gold all around them.

00:33:06.640 --> 00:33:07.458
And they had the staffs and they were standing on the side of the street and there were people of all kinds from all kinds of generations is what I'm going to say.

00:33:15.199 --> 00:33:15.399
The way they looked, on this side of the street there were what looked like English style homes that were cobblestone with beautiful roofs.

00:33:15.399 --> 00:33:32.720
It looked like something out of medieval times, but it was all perfect, the way all the grout and all the stuff was on these buildings as I can remember it even still like today, I can quote it back to you perfectly.

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:43.039
But as he was riding down, I could hear instruments playing music that was so beautiful, beyond anything I can describe to you.

00:33:43.039 --> 00:33:46.510
And they were playing behind him and they were having a parade.

00:33:46.510 --> 00:33:57.940
They were parading on this gold street and they were saying, 'For he is good and his mercy endures forever; for the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever.

00:33:57.940 --> 00:34:03.639
' And they were shouting and you could hear it and it was echoing all throughout the land.

00:34:19.419 --> 00:34:19.680
I could hear it in heaven.

00:34:19.680 --> 00:34:28.960
It was echoing and it was almost deafening how loud it was: 'For the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever.

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:35.159
' And they were saying it and they just kept saying it.

00:34:35.349 --> 00:34:37.655
And I could see this like confetti in the air.

00:34:37.655 --> 00:34:40.560
It was like beautiful stuff flying in the air all around.

00:34:40.560 --> 00:34:46.446
It was being kept all as he was marching in on his horse.

00:34:46.446 --> 00:34:48.890
They were preparing for us to come.

00:35:00.499 --> 00:35:00.880
And I could hear, 'For the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever.

00:35:00.880 --> 00:35:09.119
' And at the end of the road, I could see this massive castle that had the most beautiful sides.

00:35:09.119 --> 00:35:21.680
It was a massive castle, but there was a bridge and on this bridge I could see, going through here, I could see a stream, but on the other side of the bridge, it was the most beautiful trees and the most beautiful green grass.

00:35:27.099 --> 00:35:41.911
And there was a beautiful—all up here—a massive castle on a hill, and I still don't know what that castle is, but I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, it is the most beautiful place you can comprehend, like a gorgeous castle, and it was all kinds of stones and stuff inside this castle.

00:35:41.911 --> 00:35:45.440
But he said, 'Brandon, there's parade practice today.

00:35:45.440 --> 00:35:50.790
We're celebrating, getting ready to celebrate you.

00:35:54.480 --> 00:35:56.351
I'm getting ready to come back for my church.

00:35:57.599 --> 00:35:59.973
I'm getting ready to come back for my church.

00:35:59.973 --> 00:36:06.415
' He said, 'And all this is the reception for when you come home.

00:36:06.415 --> 00:36:12.592
' The day it happens, I saw the valleys whenever we first show up and we're raptured.

00:36:23.191 --> 00:36:24.220
I made it into heaven and I could see the beautiful green grass as far as the eye could see.

00:36:24.220 --> 00:36:28.000
And my wife was doing cartwheels and she said, 'Brandon, we made it!

00:36:28.000 --> 00:36:30.000
Brandon, we made it!

00:36:30.000 --> 00:36:32.160
It truly happened, we're here!

00:36:32.160 --> 00:36:36.400
' And she was doing cartwheels and somersaults all inside of this grass.

00:36:43.794 --> 00:36:51.839
And I was just at the top of the hill watching her roll down the hill, just excited to be there, rolling down and just rejoicing and praising the Lord that it finally had happened.

00:36:51.839 --> 00:37:01.164
I remember just looking out over the edge of it all, and there were beautiful mountains, beautiful mountains in heaven with snow on the top.

00:37:01.164 --> 00:37:02.302
Everything was gorgeous.

00:37:02.302 --> 00:37:14.240
And I remember just looking at the grass and all the flowers, and I was trying to take it in, this vision, this impartation that I was having, and I didn't want to leave it.

00:37:15.190 --> 00:37:15.380
I thought, 'Oh, God.

00:37:16.024 --> 00:37:23.680
I look for the day when he comes, ladies and gentlemen, but we have so much work to do to tell the people that he's coming.

00:37:23.680 --> 00:37:26.696
He's standing at the door of eternity.

00:37:26.696 --> 00:37:30.914
Grace as we know it is about to change.

00:37:30.914 --> 00:37:34.479
We're about to step into the tribulation.

00:37:34.479 --> 00:37:36.019
Do you understand?

00:37:36.019 --> 00:37:41.119
This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:37:41.119 --> 00:37:42.860
Tribulation is about to begin.

00:37:42.860 --> 00:37:48.457
' And that's what I try to tell you all, that I don't believe we're going through the tribulation.

00:37:48.457 --> 00:38:00.079
The church, the ones that have their lamps full of oil—there were 10 virgins, five had their lamps full and five didn't.

00:38:00.079 --> 00:38:04.760
I believe he comes back for the ones that have their lamps full.

00:38:08.617 --> 00:38:08.914
And all the beauty of the trees and the flowers.

00:38:08.914 --> 00:38:19.760
Even whenever I saw Lucy, you know, I've told you that a couple weeks ago, they were all praying and interceding for what's happening on the earth, calling for a revival.

00:38:19.760 --> 00:38:26.240
Lucy was there and Brother Halverson and there were so many others.

00:38:26.240 --> 00:38:28.180
They were on this beautiful quilt.

00:38:36.914 --> 00:38:37.383
If you have not seen that, you can watch it.

00:38:50.224 --> 00:38:50.480
It just happened a couple weeks ago when the Lord warned us about this and he said, 'They're praying for revival in Minnesota.

00:38:50.480 --> 00:38:52.690
They're praying for revival in these areas, ladies and gentlemen.

00:38:52.690 --> 00:39:00.960
' And I truly believe we're at the edge of something major that is about to take place.

00:39:10.987 --> 00:39:15.420
And as you've seen what I tried to describe to you with my English vocabulary the best I could, of what the new heaven and the new earth, what he is creating for us for the thousand years, is the most beautiful.

00:39:15.420 --> 00:39:18.631
We've never experienced anything like the lion and the lamb lying together.

00:39:18.631 --> 00:39:21.810
We've never experienced not experiencing death or pain or suffering of any kind.

00:39:21.810 --> 00:39:25.040
Some people wake up with a headache, some people might wake up with a toothache.

00:39:25.040 --> 00:39:25.600
Who knows?

00:39:25.600 --> 00:39:28.091
We all have a body that is dying every day.

00:39:28.091 --> 00:39:33.080
We get closer and closer to the day we're going home.

00:39:33.080 --> 00:39:40.020
But when we have our glorified body and we're over there with the Father, oh, what a day!

00:39:55.634 --> 00:39:56.046
You know, what a day of rejoicing that will be when we all get to heaven, we'll sing and shout the victory.

00:39:56.046 --> 00:40:02.340
When we all get to heaven, what a day of rejoicing that will be.

00:40:02.340 --> 00:40:05.790
When we all see Jesus, we'll sing and shout the victory.

00:40:05.790 --> 00:40:07.290
Those old hymns mean something.

00:40:07.290 --> 00:40:11.320
They weren't written to win a Dove Award; they were written just because they wanted to worship Jesus.

00:40:13.320 --> 00:40:13.730
I still pull them out.

00:40:13.730 --> 00:40:20.779
My wife got me an old song book because I like to look at those old songs.

00:40:20.779 --> 00:40:27.542
But the most important part today is knowing that we're so close to something major about to happen.

00:40:30.471 --> 00:40:43.200
And I tell you all this to fan that flame inside of you, to give you a hope, that even if Charlie wanted to come back—you know, people said, 'Brandon, raise him from the dead.

00:40:43.200 --> 00:40:46.220
' He stepped over; he was over there too long, folks.

00:40:46.220 --> 00:40:47.467
Do you understand?

00:40:47.467 --> 00:40:52.926
It'd be like pulling teeth to try to get him to come back.

00:41:04.079 --> 00:41:12.267
Once you experience the glory, once you experience the splendor and the majesty of heaven, the smells, the fragrances, the beauty of what he has for us, with just the glimpses that I've been given that I've treasured for so long, I'll never forget it.

00:41:25.840 --> 00:41:26.240
It's like Diana says, when she had a visitation the other night, she said, "I didn't want to wake up from it.

00:41:26.240 --> 00:41:29.030
" Things that we don't share publicly.

00:41:30.980 --> 00:41:32.240
"I didn't want to wake up from it.

00:41:35.440 --> 00:41:37.520
I just wanted to stay there.

00:41:38.770 --> 00:41:39.020
I fought so bad.

00:41:39.020 --> 00:41:46.549
Please don't let me wake up from this because it was such a beautiful encounter with the Father.

00:41:46.549 --> 00:41:48.502
" God is no respecter of persons.

00:41:52.320 --> 00:42:00.930
And the same Holy Spirit that visits us, and the visitations that my wife and I have, and my children have, I'm telling you, He'll visit you.

00:42:00.930 --> 00:42:02.608
He loves every single one of you.

00:42:02.608 --> 00:42:06.000
He loves every single one of us unconditionally.

00:42:17.599 --> 00:42:18.717
But if you don't know Him tonight, and I'm telling you all this, and you say, "How do I get to go?

00:42:18.717 --> 00:42:23.306
What pays my ticket to go to heaven?

00:42:23.306 --> 00:42:23.511
How do I?

00:42:23.511 --> 00:42:29.573
" It's by accepting Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

00:42:41.947 --> 00:42:42.213
It's by dying to self and saying, "Jesus, I don't want any more of the world.

00:42:50.639 --> 00:42:52.720
I want You.

00:42:55.160 --> 00:42:56.676
I want to tell people about You.

00:42:56.844 --> 00:43:01.329
I want to lead them to Christ just like I'm being led to Christ right now.

00:43:10.671 --> 00:43:10.847
I want to tell them that there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:43:16.373 --> 00:43:20.782
" If you're here tonight and you don't know Jesus, you've heard a lot about Him, but does He know you?

00:43:20.782 --> 00:43:24.166
That's the bottom line.

00:43:24.166 --> 00:43:28.710
Does Jesus know you?

00:43:28.720 --> 00:43:33.791
The Bible says in that day that many will come and say, "Lord, I prophesied in Your name.

00:43:34.368 --> 00:43:35.520
I laid hands on the sick in Your name.

00:43:36.480 --> 00:43:37.344
I cast out devils in Your name.

00:43:37.728 --> 00:43:38.688
" And He says, "Depart from me.

00:43:50.799 --> 00:43:53.360
I never knew you.

00:43:54.773 --> 00:43:55.413
" You could do all those things.

00:44:15.279 --> 00:44:15.546
And I've said this a lot.

00:44:15.546 --> 00:44:21.920
It takes a little faith to raise the dead.

00:44:21.920 --> 00:44:26.826
It takes some faith to cast out a devil.

00:44:26.826 --> 00:44:39.040
But you can do all those things and He can say to you, "Depart from me.

00:44:43.848 --> 00:44:44.151
I never knew you.

00:44:44.151 --> 00:44:45.057
" It's Scripture.

00:44:45.057 --> 00:44:46.924
Does He know you?

00:44:46.924 --> 00:44:49.432
Does He have a relationship with you?

00:44:49.432 --> 00:44:50.536
I'm not talking about works.

00:44:50.536 --> 00:44:55.840
I'm not talking about something you tried to do to impress Him.

00:44:55.840 --> 00:45:03.069
"By grace you are saved through faith, not of works, lest any man should boast.

00:45:03.069 --> 00:45:08.720
" It is by grace.

00:45:08.720 --> 00:45:12.000
But I want to tell you it's about a relationship.

00:45:12.000 --> 00:45:14.740
It's about Him knowing you.

00:45:26.620 --> 00:45:26.960
And if you're here today and you say, "I don't want to go to hell, Brandon.

00:45:26.960 --> 00:45:31.075
I don't want to go to hell.

00:45:31.075 --> 00:45:36.720
I'm having a really hard time right now.

00:45:36.720 --> 00:45:39.089
All people are dying on the news.

00:45:39.089 --> 00:45:42.480
You've got cops getting shot in the throat.

00:45:42.480 --> 00:45:47.156
You've got stuff going on in Chicago.

00:45:47.156 --> 00:45:50.880
You've got war going on, rumors of war.

00:45:50.880 --> 00:45:52.311
You've got the war in Israel.

00:45:52.311 --> 00:45:55.173
You've got all these things.

00:45:55.173 --> 00:45:59.627
" And it's very troubling to the natural mind.

00:45:59.627 --> 00:46:00.666
Very troubling.

00:46:00.666 --> 00:46:05.371
If you focus on it, it tries to suck you in.

00:46:09.840 --> 00:46:12.940
But I'm here to tell you that Jesus Christ paid the price for you not to have to go to hell.

00:46:12.940 --> 00:46:20.047
Jesus paid the price for you to not have to have sickness in your body.

00:46:20.047 --> 00:46:27.028
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory in every area of your life.

00:46:27.028 --> 00:46:30.640
But you have never surrendered to Him is what I'm trying to say.

00:46:30.640 --> 00:46:32.640
"I surrender to You.

00:46:35.420 --> 00:46:35.690
I make You my Lord.

00:46:35.690 --> 00:46:39.931
I turn my back on the world and I say I'm all in tonight.

00:46:39.931 --> 00:46:46.170
" I want to give you an opportunity to accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

00:46:46.170 --> 00:46:59.653
I tell you all these beautiful things that are awaiting the believer—for the person who says, "I'm sold out to Jesus"—the ones when you spend time with Him daily, then He knows you.

00:46:59.653 --> 00:47:02.107
That's how you know your wife.

00:47:02.107 --> 00:47:04.740
That's how you know your husband, right?

00:47:04.740 --> 00:47:10.240
The more you spend time with them, you can say, "I really know him or her," right?

00:47:19.138 --> 00:47:19.422
"I know them.

00:47:19.422 --> 00:47:40.053
" But if I don't spend time with my wife but once a month or once a year, maybe every once in a while when church is there on Sundays, they'll have an Easter service and I'll go just because it's the right thing to do on an Easter or a Sunday—or a Christmas service, a candlelight service.

00:47:40.053 --> 00:47:43.240
We all go as a family because we just want to celebrate Jesus's birth.

00:47:43.240 --> 00:47:44.986
"Let's go and have a candlelight service.

00:47:52.840 --> 00:47:53.140
" But other than that, you don't ever go through the doorway of a church.

00:47:53.140 --> 00:47:55.687
You're just off in La La Land.

00:47:55.687 --> 00:47:58.800
I'm talking about the people who are sold out.

00:47:58.800 --> 00:48:01.314
He said, "If you're lukewarm, I'll spew you out of my mouth.

00:48:01.314 --> 00:48:03.200
" He'd rather you be hot or cold.

00:48:03.200 --> 00:48:07.271
"If you're lukewarm, He'll spew you out of His mouth.

00:48:13.773 --> 00:48:14.107
" It's time to be hot for Jesus or be cold.

00:48:24.990 --> 00:48:25.200
If you don't want to be in it, don't ride the fence is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:48:25.200 --> 00:48:26.836
There's no lukewarm.

00:48:26.836 --> 00:48:29.260
It's time to be all in.

00:48:36.026 --> 00:48:36.248
We are in the last of the last seconds here before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:48:36.248 --> 00:48:48.116
He even told Rodney—I was listening to a revival in Tulsa here at the center, and he said the Lord told him we have a window, and he went up into 2028, 2029.

00:48:48.116 --> 00:48:59.520
He was saying the Lord told him He gave him a window in 2020 about the COVID and all the things going on.

00:48:59.520 --> 00:49:05.306
He said there was a whirlwind that whipped him up, and he got sucked up.

00:49:15.707 --> 00:49:15.973
And the Lord told him, "I'm giving you a 10-year window.

00:49:17.039 --> 00:49:18.132
" And what have I told you all?

00:49:31.680 --> 00:49:31.920
The next Shemitah cycle.

00:49:32.639 --> 00:49:33.119
The next Shemitah cycle.

00:49:33.119 --> 00:49:38.891
There are a lot of people who say, "I believe it's the 23rd.

00:49:38.891 --> 00:49:42.160
I believe it's the next Shemitah cycle," which would be 2028 going into '29.

00:49:50.448 --> 00:49:50.864
It's that time frame.

00:50:06.649 --> 00:50:06.979
And I believe the Lord has given us a three-year window for a major harvest right now.

00:50:10.280 --> 00:50:10.609
And on a scale of eternity, that is nothing.

00:50:10.609 --> 00:50:11.269
Nothing.

00:50:11.269 --> 00:50:14.009
What will you do with this window of opportunity?

00:50:18.469 --> 00:50:18.880
The Lord said, "A great shaking to awaken is here.

00:50:18.880 --> 00:50:37.420
" And I'm telling you, if you're here right now and you feel that tugging on the inside of you—and as I've told you all, you feel that stirring on the inside of you—and you say, "Brandon, what must I do to be saved?

00:50:37.420 --> 00:50:38.570
" Do you feel that?

00:50:45.108 --> 00:50:45.440
The Bible says that no man comes to the Father unless he's drawn by Him.

00:50:47.359 --> 00:50:50.639
And if you feel that inside, that's the Holy Spirit tugging at your heart.

00:50:50.639 --> 00:50:54.148
He's at the door of your life and He's knocking.

00:50:54.148 --> 00:50:55.616
"Will you let me help you?

00:50:55.616 --> 00:50:58.720
Will you let me change you from the inside out?

00:50:58.720 --> 00:50:59.733
" You're broke.

00:50:59.733 --> 00:51:00.373
You're busted.

00:51:00.373 --> 00:51:01.013
You're disgusted.

00:51:01.013 --> 00:51:02.674
Your marriage is strung out.

00:51:02.674 --> 00:51:03.793
You're on drugs.

00:51:03.793 --> 00:51:04.960
You're strung out on alcohol.

00:51:11.169 --> 00:51:11.359
You've got all these problems of sexual perversion.

00:51:11.359 --> 00:51:19.794
You've got all these things, and you're trying to fix it yourself.

00:51:19.794 --> 00:51:27.316
But Jesus Christ wants to fix your issues and help you turn your mess into a message.

00:51:27.316 --> 00:51:33.340
I believe it's appointed unto man once to die, and after that the judgment.

00:51:33.340 --> 00:51:35.320
I don't believe in reincarnation.

00:51:35.320 --> 00:51:40.288
I don't believe in any other kind of religion other than Jesus Christ.

00:51:40.288 --> 00:51:42.1000
He's the only way.

00:51:51.920 --> 00:51:52.222
The only way to the Father is the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:51:52.222 --> 00:51:56.208
So I want you today to make a decision.

00:52:09.040 --> 00:52:10.020
I want you to make a decision either way.

00:52:55.555 --> 00:52:56.572
You either serve Him or you don't.

00:52:56.572 --> 00:53:01.1000
It's your choice.

00:53:01.1000 --> 00:53:14.373
But I pray today you make the right choice.

00:53:36.559 --> 00:53:38.040
I pray today that you say, "I'm sold out for Jesus.

00:53:38.040 --> 00:53:46.192
" What more do you have?

00:53:46.192 --> 00:53:57.223
I believe it's a heaven to gain or a hell to shun.

00:53:57.223 --> 00:53:58.617
Do you understand?

00:53:58.617 --> 00:54:00.079
There's no in-between.

00:54:00.079 --> 00:54:04.274
"Well, I believe we go into nothingness.

00:54:04.274 --> 00:54:07.620
I believe we turn into a dove.

00:54:07.620 --> 00:54:14.448
" I've heard all kinds of crazy stuff, and I just go, "No.

00:54:26.391 --> 00:54:26.693
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord, or being present in hell.

00:54:26.693 --> 00:54:39.050
" The moment you die, the very shoes you put on today to go to work or whatever, the undertaker might be taking them off that evening.

00:54:39.050 --> 00:54:43.645
No man knows the day that he's going to go home.

00:54:43.645 --> 00:54:45.626
No man knows.

00:54:56.800 --> 00:54:57.360
A lot of people might think they know, but nobody truly knows.

00:54:57.360 --> 00:55:04.189
I'm going to tell you, I want you to accept Jesus Christ right now.

00:55:21.839 --> 00:55:22.182
And I'm going to say this prayer, but I want you to put in the comment section right now, "I need to be saved.

00:55:22.182 --> 00:55:28.120
